Product Description
HP Elite Mini 800 G9 PC 
The HP Elite Mini 800 G9 provides users with the commercial-grade performance, security, and the flexible deployment capabilities needed for small, varied workspaces. This reliable, ultra-small PC is powered to handle mainstream enterprise and SMBs with an 14th Gen Intel Core i7-14700 20-Core processor and protected with always-on security you can trust. 
14th Gen Intel Core i7-14700 2.1 GHz 20-Core LGA 1700 Processor. Built with the Intel 7 process, this 14th generation desktop processor delivers improved power efficiency with a total of 20 cores while fitting the LGA 1700 socket. Featuring an optimized Hybrid Core Architecture, the Core i7-14700 powers demanding applications and games with eight 2.1 GHz Performance-cores, while the 12 low-voltage Efficient-cores handle background tasks for smooth multitasking. The built-in Intel Thread Director ensures that the two work seamlessly together by dynamically and intelligently assigning workloads to the right core at the right time. With 33MB of cache and a 5.4 GHz Turbo Boost Max 3.0 frequency, this processor is made to handle intense workloads. 
The integrated Intel UHD Graphics 770 chipset delivers a sharp, clear picture, and you'll be able to output video using the HDMI 2.1 and DisplayPort 1.4a outputs. Connect to the internet via Wi-Fi 6 (802.11ax), or use the Gigabit Ethernet jack for a more stable and reliable wired connection.

CHAMPION CHIP — The M4 chip brings spectacular speed and capability to blaze through everyday activities and multitask across multiple productivity and pro apps.

ALL-DAY BATTERY LIFE — MacBook Pro delivers the same exceptional performance whether it’s running on battery or plugged in.
APPS FLY WITH APPLE SILICON — All your favorites, including Microsoft 365 and Adobe Creative Cloud, run lightning fast in macOS.*

IF YOU LOVE IPHONE, YOU’LL LOVE MAC — Mac works like magic with your other Apple devices. View and control what’s on your iPhone from your Mac with iPhone Mirroring.* Copy something on iPhone and paste it on Mac. Send texts with Messages or use your Mac to answer FaceTime calls.*

ADVANCED CAMERA AND AUDIO — Stay perfectly framed and sound great with a 12MP Center Stage camera, three studio-quality mics, and six speakers with Spatial Audio and support for Dolby Atmos.
CONNECT IT ALL — This MacBook Pro features three Thunderbolt 4 ports and a MagSafe 3 charging port, SDXC card slot, HDMI port, and headphone jack. And it supports up to two external displays.
